Day 54 – Road to Fluent Spanish Summary

Today’s Spanish study session focused heavily on practical conversational fluency, travel vocabulary, recommendation phrases, shopping/cost questions, and continued review of Pimsleur Unit 2 Lesson 10. Strong emphasis was placed on improving automatic sentence recall, conversational response speed, and handling longer real-world dialogue structures without relying on notes.

