el boleto = ticket
Memrise Review:
Focused on practical conversational and shopping-related vocabulary:

¿Cuánto cuesta? = How much does it cost?
¿Cuánto cuestan tres boletos? = How much do three tickets cost?
¿Cuánto cuesta este libro? = How much does this book cost?
¿Cuánto cuestan estos? = How much do these cost?
¿Cuánto dinero tienes? = How much money do you have?
enviarlo = to send it
no puedo enviarlo = I can’t send it
buscar = to look for
por allí = over there
